Hardware Requirements

Arduino Board: (e.g., Uno, Mega, etc.)

MPU6050 Sensor Module

SSD1306 OLED Display (128x64)

Push Buttons:
i)One for menu navigation (MENU_BTN connected to digital pin 3)
ii)One for selection/enter (ENTER_BTN connected to digital pin 4)

Miscellaneous:
Breadboard and jumper wires for prototyping
